{"id": "1428302149703569530", "channel_id": "1400749543288475770", "author_id": "220456612698128384", "author_name": "sleepypillow", "content": "I have not used Ghelot myself prior to act 8 so I can only make somewhat educates guesses.\n\nMouse Wisdom for now. \nUnlock Festival of Tides from Myriam's Dreamscape *Desecrate* and use that until you finished act 7. It costs 7 Reality Verges but is one of the best general posses in the game. \nThere are some cool caro posses but they all delete your health even further and you have no good way of healing back up without e2 thais/act7 posse duplicating your ghelot flails.\n If you ever get e2 Thais before act 8,  you can use Uvash's Posse  *Roaring Blood and Sand*. Maybe she reruns during anniversary. It is very advised to pick her up and get her to e2. \nSomewhat the most important awakener in the game. \n\nIf anyone else has better idea's for posses in this specific circumstance, feel free to educate me.", "timestamp": "2025-10-16T08:42:49.060000+00:00", "type": 19, "edited_timestamp": "2025-10-16T08:55:03.252000+00:00", "mentions": ["1143857926168129546"], "reply_to": "1428296409924501546"}
